	<h2>
			CNV relembra os 50 anos e investiga o Massacre de Ipatinga		</h2>








        <div style="clear:both;"></div>
        <div class="itp-share">

                	<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://cnv.memoriasreveladas.gov.br/outros-destaques/351-cnv-relembra-e-investiga-os-50-anos-do-massacre-de-ipatinga.html" data-text="CNV relembra os 50 anos e investiga o Massacre de Ipatinga" data-via="" data-lang="pt" data-size="small" data-related="" data-hashtags="" data-count="none"><img src="file://///mecsrv01/portalmec_dev/www/cnv/site/templates/cnv/images/btn_twitter.png" />Tweet</a><div class="itp-share-fbl">
